    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，五个状态加一个入口。Pending之后应该是进入Processing对吧？那从Processing到Completed是用MarkOrderCompleteCMD吗？另外Cancelled只能从Processing触发吗？",
