      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出主流程：Ingress Controller → Pending → Processing → Completed，加上Processing → Cancelled的分支。接下来Error状态怎么接入？是Processing也可能出错吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "state_OrderPending",
        "state_OrderProcessing",
        "state_OrderCompleted",
        "state_OrderCancelled",
