      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "这里有个特殊设计：MarkOrderCompleteCMD在Processing阶段如果执行失败，会进入Error状态而不是Completed。所以Processing到Error也是MarkOrderCompleteCMD这条边，表示执行异常的情况。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "state_OrderProcessing",
        "state_OrderError",
        "state_OrderCompleted",
